attributionInfo.brokerName: Hill Country Home And Land LLC

data.description: Gorgeous home in the highly sought after community of Fair Oaks Ranch (Estate Section). Close access to Country Club ( golf, tennis, pools, gym, playground, dining, etc.). Stately, immaculate 5 or 6 BR Family Home with 2 Living Areas. Expansive Master Suite with His & Hers Walk-in Closets, Enormous Master Bath 17 X 12 with dual vanities, garden tub, separate shower and Secondary Bedroom on 1st Floor(In-Law-Suite) with Full Bath. Huge Gourmet Kitchen,  Oversized Double Island, Chef's Pantry, Family Room w/Fireplace, Dining Room, Office Space, 3 Car Garage with Built-In-Cupboards. Second Floor with Living Space and 4 Bedrooms( or 3 with Media Room) and 2 Full Baths. Superb Coveted Patio with Huge Back Yard for Entertaining ( fireplace area, possibility of pool, etc.) Which is uncommon in this Prestige Neighborhood. Located minutes off of I 10 with shopping close by.
